snippet.title: The Da Vinci Code (2006 Video Game) - Intro
snippet.description: Intro of The Da Vinci Code, an action-adventure puzzle video game developed by The Collective and published by 2K Games on May 19, 2006 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 2 and Xbox.
